column2: @AndieNft @CanineCartelNFT Wow congrats!
@JaxsonZara @dj_rstar This person is a scammer

Stay vigilant friends. Oh, and here's a list of everyone else who i messaged so you can check out their accounts for red flags. There's even more if you check who all reacted to this tweet: https://t.co/ZsKR8DcjQX https://t.co/BF9jms68Qn

Thankfully, I ended the situation with a laugh and no lost money. But truth be told, I got lucky. If the other scammers didn't all cannibalize Emily's con I really might have fell for it. I'm happy to have learned this lesson the easy way and am sharing so you all can too.
'She' even sent me a video flipping the image like a card so i could see how legit it was. You really can't make this stuff up. https://t.co/bH5JOyuV8d
SHE SENT ME THIS ü§£ ‚Äî she quite literally pulled the 2d image from above into blender and tried to pass it off as a 3d model. https://t.co/FYiDPWEKa1
At this point I knew she was a scammer, but I had to see what would happen. https://t.co/VaXY9XV2TL

So now i asked Emily to provide me an instagram. I checked it out and it seemed very obvious that she had not made any of the art on it. So i asked her to simply provide me with a screenshot of one of her 3d models in blender so i could see she actually built it.

It was immediately clear they were all scammers. None could provide portfolios or links to their work. only photos. mostly watermarked. two even provided the SAME art as 'theirs'. https://t.co/9YJHgPdAe8

but theennnn i woke up the next morning and something fishy had happened. 7 (and counting) other accounts with pretty girls in their PFPs and similar bios had messaged me in similar ways. Things are getting fishy. I start messaging them to see whats up.
I explained the work i needed and she graciously provided some references. And she was very eager to start on the work promising a quick turnaround. https://t.co/wsWeVrABZO
I first posted a tweet looking for 3D artists and Emily below was kind enough to respond. https://t.co/DVr65fVDEc
Look out for scammers everyone, here's a short thread/fun story...
You guys try listening to a Gary Vee podcast lately? Shit is fire.
If I have any 3D artists in my network please hit me up!
